<template>
  <section>
    asdasdasd
  </section>
</template>

<script>
import axios from 'axios';

export default {
  data(){
    return{
      order_data:[],
      status_data:undefined,
    }
  },
  methods:{
    async get_orders(){
      await axios.get("http://localhost:8080/api/orders", {withCredentials:true})
      .then(res => {this.order_data = res.data.order; this.status_data = res.data.status; console.log(res.data.order)});      
    }
  },
  mounted(){
    this.get_orders().then(console.log(this.status_data));
  }
}
</script>
